Py Modules:
Module- Py file acting as module.

variables,functins, classes:module Members

inbuilt modules and user defined modules.

How to import modules members? import,from and as keywords
========================================================
import module1,module2...
import module1 as m1, module2 as m2...

from module import member1,member2,member3
from module import member1 as m1,member2 as m2,member3 as m3

from module import *

user.py  - module name:  user
user-defined module

